# Spotify API Credentials
# Get these from https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard

SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_spotify_client_id_here
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_spotify_client_secret_here
SPOTIFY_REFRESH_TOKEN=your_spotify_refresh_token_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual Spotify app credentials
# 3. Use scripts/generate-refresh-token.js to get your refresh token
# 4. For production deployment, set these as environment variables in your hosting platform